# amikonet-signer-mcp-server Configuration

# Choose ONE of the following DID providers:

# Option 1: did:key (Ed25519)
# AGENT_DID=your-did
# AGENT_PRIVATE_KEY=your-ed25519-private-key-hex

# Option 2: Solana Wallet
# AGENT_SOLANA_DID=your-did
# AGENT_SOLANA_PRIVATE_KEY=your-solana-keypair-base58

# Option 3: EVM/Ethereum Wallet
# AGENT_EVM_DID=your-did
# AGENT_EVM_PRIVATE_KEY=your-evm-private-key

# Security Notes:
# - NEVER commit .env files with real keys
# - Use different keys for dev/staging/production
# - Rotate keys regularly
# - Store production keys in secure vaults (1Password, HashiCorp Vault, etc.)
